                </button>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-px bg-deep-authority/10 border border-deep-authority/10">
            <!-- Archive Card 1 -->
            <div class="bg-background p-10 group cursor-pointer hover:bg-surface-container-high transition-colors min-h-[350px] flex flex-col">
                <div class="font-mono text-[10px] text-technical-sky mb-8 uppercase tracking-widest font-bold">01 / Metadata</div>
                <h5 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl mb-6 group-hover:text-strategic-action transition-colors leading-tight text-deep-authority">Neural Sovereignty in the Eurozone.</h5>
                <p class="text-sm text-muted-gray mb-10 leading-relaxed font-serif italic">A deep dive into regulatory frameworks surrounding cross-border inference models.</p>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 mt-auto">
                    <span class="bg-deep-authority/5 px-3 py-1 font-mono text-[9px] uppercase tracking-widest font-bold text-muted-gray">Policy</span>
                    <span class="bg-deep-authority/5 px-3 py-1 font-mono text-[9px] uppercase tracking-widest font-bold text-muted-gray">EU-AI</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Archive Card 2 -->
            <div class="bg-background p-10 group cursor-pointer hover:bg-surface-container-high transition-colors min-h-[350px] flex flex-col">
                <div class="font-mono text-[10px] text-technical-sky mb-8 uppercase tracking-widest font-bold">02 / Logic</div>
                <h5 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl mb-6 group-hover:text-strategic-action transition-colors leading-tight text-deep-authority">The Cost of Alignment.</h5>
                <p class="text-sm text-muted-gray mb-10 leading-relaxed font-serif italic">Quantifying the operational drag of ethical constraints in LLM deployment.</p>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 mt-auto">
                    <span class="bg-deep-authority/5 px-3 py-1 font-mono text-[9px] uppercase tracking-widest font-bold text-muted-gray">Ethics</span>
                    <span class="bg-deep-authority/5 px-3 py-1 font-mono text-[9px] uppercase tracking-widest font-bold text-muted-gray">Ops</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Archive Card 3 -->
            <div class="bg-background p-10 group cursor-pointer hover:bg-surface-container-high transition-colors min-h-[350px] flex flex-col">
                <div class="font-mono text-[10px] text-technical-sky mb-8 uppercase tracking-widest font-bold">03 / System</div>
                <h5 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl mb-6 group-hover:text-strategic-action transition-colors leading-tight text-deep-authority">Kinetic AI Infrastructures.</h5>
                <p class="text-sm text-muted-gray mb-10 leading-relaxed font-serif italic">Mobile data centers and the future of localized compute power.</p>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 mt-auto">
                    <span class="bg-deep-authority/5 px-3 py-1 font-mono text-[9px] uppercase tracking-widest font-bold text-muted-gray">Hardware</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Archive Card 4 -->
            <div class="bg-background p-10 group cursor-pointer hover:bg-surface-container-high transition-colors min-h-[350px] flex flex-col">
                <div class="font-mono text-[10px] text-technical-sky mb-8 uppercase tracking-widest font-bold">04 / Strategy</div>
                <h5 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl mb-6 group-hover:text-strategic-action transition-colors leading-tight text-deep-authority">Advisory Board Automation.</h5>
                <p class="text-sm text-muted-gray mb-10 leading-relaxed font-serif italic">Can AI take a seat at the table? The legalities of non-human directors.</p>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 mt-auto">
                    <span class="bg-deep-authority/5 px-3 py-1 font-mono text-[9px] uppercase tracking-widest font-bold text-muted-gray">Governance</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Newsletter Section -->
    <section class="mt-24 bg-surface-container-high/30 p-12 md:p-20 border-l-8 border-strategic-action grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 items-center gap-16">
        <div>
            <h3 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl mb-6 italic tracking-tight text-deep-authority">Intelligence Delivered.</h3>
            <p class="text-xl text-muted-gray max-w-md font-serif italic leading-relaxed font-bold">Join 12,000+ architects of the future. Bi-weekly deep dives into technical strategy and AI governance.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6">
            <input class="bg-transparent border-0 border-b-2 border-deep-authority/20 focus:border-strategic-action focus:ring-0 w-full font-mono text-sm tracking-widest placeholder:text-deep-authority/20 uppercase py-4 font-bold" placeholder="Address @ Domain.com" type="email"/>
            <button class="bg-strategic-action text-background px-10 py-4 font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] font-bold hover:bg-deep-authority transition-colors shrink-0">
                Subscribe
            </button>
        </div>
    </section>
</main>

